channel.title: Looking for
channel.description:
I'm looking for this game I saw a while ago but I have no clue what the name was, a while as in a year or 1/2 year, I don't know, I don't remember.
It was a bit like Crysis 2, there was an alien invasion and I remember in the trailer that you had to fight in a city that was being taken over and you had to shoot big aliens and stuff, it had great graphics from what I remember.
If anyone knows what I'm talking about or has an idea, please post a comment.
